# Example bet message formats and how they're interpreted:
# @book-dk 0.5u 50% nfl bonus:free_bet          -> Uses a free bet bonus on DraftKings
# @book-dk 0.5u 50% nfl use:odds_boost          -> Uses an odds boost on DraftKings
# @book-fd 1u mlb bonus:25%_boost               -> Uses a 25% odds boost on FanDuel
# @book-mgm 0.25u nba                           -> Standard bet on BetMGM (no bonus)
# "@book-fd 1u MLB This looks good with no sweat HR" -> Uses a "no sweat home run" promo
# "@book-dk 2u 20% MLB"                         -> Uses a 20% MLB-specific boost if available
